---

This package bundles statically-linked builds of the following third-party
C libraries. Each retains its original license; copies of those licenses
ship inside their respective vendored source trees during the build.

- libgit2 (https://github.com/libgit2/libgit2) — GPLv2 with linking exception
- libssh2 (https://www.libssh2.org/) — BSD-3-Clause
- OpenSSL (https://www.openssl.org/) — Apache-2.0 (3.0.0 and later)
- PCRE (https://pcre.org/) — BSD-3-Clause

The build script `build-libgit2-framework.sh` orchestrates downloading,
building, and combining these libraries into a single XCFramework.
